**  ER (ERROR-MESSAGE)
E-01 ENTER DATE
E-02 DATE IS NOT CORRECT
E-03 ENTER CREATE DAY
E-04 <*> OR BLANK IS INTO REVERSING AREA
E-05 <S,M,E> OR BLANK IS INTO REVERSING AREA
E-06 <R> OR BLANK IS INTO REVERSING AREA
E-07 EITHER OF <0,1,2> IS INTO THERE
E-08 <0,1,2> IS INTO REVERSING AREA
E-09 DATE IS NOT CORRECT
E-10 THERE ISN'T ON THE DATE
E-11 EXISTS ALREADY
**  AA1/BB2
1MONDAY
2TUESDAY
3WEDNSDAY
4THURSDAY
5FRIDAY
6SATURDAY
7SUNDAY
**  TB1/TB2
0 CANCEL
1 CHANGE
2 ADD
